* Iron Raptor looks from the new bot to Fliq, nodding when he repeats the 
orders she'd given him before.
Even though he hadn't followed him she wasn't disappointed, her expression 
not changing one bit.*

" Then take him to quarters until further notice, you can keep him company. 
And I expect you to follow those orders this time."

* She looked up at the new transformer.*

" No offence, but you're right. You can't be too careful and after being 
attacked just now I think I have a right to keep a close eye on you. But it 
won't last forever."

* Iron Raptor then slipped into the controle room without further notice, 
the door closing behind her.*
